### ============================================
### 4. ACTUALIZAR ESTUDIANTE PARCIAL (PATCH) - v2
### Solo actualizará los campos que envíes
### ============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/student/patch/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{studentId}}",
  "nombre": "Juan Carlos Pérez",
  "edad": 23
}

### Ejemplo: Solo cambiar el correo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/student/patch/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{studentId}}",
  "correo": "nuevo.correo@example.com"
}

### Ejemplo: Cambiar múltiples campos
PATCH {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/student/patch/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{studentId}}",
  "telefono": "3201112222",
  "ciudadResidencia": "Cali"
}

### ============================================
### 5. ELIMINAR ESTUDIANTE (DELETE) - v2
### ============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/student/delete/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

